videos.description: Zach LaVine drives right and pulls up to splash a high-arcing 3-pointer over the extended hands of Luguentz Dort.
videos.headline: LaVine splashes difficult pull-up 3-pointer

videos.description: Zach LaVine races down the court for a 3-pointer, but comes up empty as the Thunder come back to defeat the Bulls 127-125 in overtime.
